data.description: Charming cottage perfect for first home, investment property or downsize home just 5 minutes from beautiful downtown Columbia. One level Brick, 2/1 plus possible 3rd bedroom, dining room or office. Nice hardwood floors. Metal Roof, refrigerator and stove are only a couple of years old! Storage with doors underneath house. Nice playground only steps away (maintained by city). Good sized yard includes raised garden with flowers, herbs and vegetables. Only 2 minutes to Hwy 43 (Bypass) providing easy access to Interstate and Nashville Hwy to Spring Hill/Franklin/Nashville.
